Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The controls aren't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're being washed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the rift between the dimensions...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear the moaning of twisted space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the dissonance of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time before we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to Union again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't! Your body can't handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we Union, I'll be able to hear the scale that the dimensions play on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the flow carry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harmonize with the sounds around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you feel it, my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be my last Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resounding Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{no op}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.34,0:01:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have something very important to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is a story of 12,000 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and of another 12,000 years before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An eternal saga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to listen to stories when we could be helping Amata{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on top of a book!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This book was always with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has come to us from ages past,\Nyet too, it has never moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is called the Book of Twin Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, at long last...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shall be opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story begins 24,000 long years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These visions are more lifelike than my Prophecies of Despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let this sword be like a tuning fork...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its resonance will point me to the exit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those images?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tuning fork is calling out the memories etched into the dimensions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dark Angels were humanity's great enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They brought immeasurable \Ndestruction and took innumerable lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The footsteps of doom were approaching...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and their owner's name was Apollonius, the Angel of Slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But by some strange trick of fate, he found love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius fell in love with a human woman, Celiane, though she was his enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius piloted a Machine Angel to drive away the Dark Angels
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and protect Celiane and her world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for every light, there is a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius' betrothed, the Dark Angel Toma,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,both loved him still and hated him for his betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there was another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A small one who sought light from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the Winged Hound Pollon, Apollonius' companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He bore an unrequited love for Celiane, who loved his master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sorrowful Pollon made a wish to the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If we were to be reborn, may Celiane and I be reunited."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many emotions, including Toma's hatred and Pollon's wishes, were left as time flowed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The void left by the dead. The sorrow felt by the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joy in the shadows, and madness in the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us bring them all together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wrap them up with beautiful lace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The noon sun is life, and the nighttime moon is death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They blur together, until...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second chapter is beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These visions again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the same as the ones we saw before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dark Angels returned from their long absence,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and plagued humanity once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But humanity still remembered the legend of their salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is High Commander Fudo there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were seeing what happened 12,000 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch! This is the very center of the legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The humans followed their legends, unearthed the Machine Angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and used it to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Apollonius' place, Aquarion had a new pilot:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy named Apollo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! He was Apollonius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was the reincarnation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was actually the reincarnation of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura! Taking the true Eve for yourself is an act of outright treason!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You no longer have the right to call yourself a citizen of Altair!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone have Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:08:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo was the reincarnation of the Winged Hound Pollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollon from the legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the reincarnation of a winged dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His love, Celiane, was reincarnated as Silvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two were brought together by a twist of fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and an attraction formed between them on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But fate can also be cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the Dark Angel Toma was also reborn into that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma still bore love and hatred for Apollonius,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he schemed to destroy the humanity that Apollonius fought for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his twisted love brought about the destruction of his own kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tree of Life meant to restore the Dark Angels
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did not bear fruit, but withered and fell back into the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again in 12,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let human and Angel join hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and forge a new Genesis for this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poor Winged Hound, Pollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For before his love of 12,000 years could be realized,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he would have to be separated once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the day the world began.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, the legend lept forward another 12,000 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into the third chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third chapter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third chapter takes place now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world split!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Tree of Life withered, the world fell out of balance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the planet was divided in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark and light. Positive and negative. Male and female.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two opposite worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two lover stars separated by the Milky Way, Vega and Altair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth, and the other Earth beyond the Dimension Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and its opposite world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were originally one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it was God playing dice,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or perhaps some form of quantum entanglement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two worlds' fates were linked, despite their separation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:11:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two worlds that are fragments. Two souls ripped away from one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the story in the Book of Twin Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their world wants ours, just like I wanted Amata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two worlds bound by fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can almost hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final melody I've been searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two worlds that long for one another sing two melodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade is lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're trying to reach each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to fill the gaps in each others' hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:12:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over the eons, Pollon became Apollo, then a new form.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was born to a songstress of Vega, Alicia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another had reached this age first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrying all his memories from all the ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo was never Apollonius.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have my revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He divided the soul of Alicia's child in two,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,plotting to use it to take his revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And though Apollo's soul was so divided,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:13:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the part of Celiane that loved and became Silvia was reborn into just one life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would that be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who has inherited Silvia's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata really is part of Apollo's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me the intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world divided into two worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo's soul divided into two lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a legend of tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tragedy has a director.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A soul haunted by his terribly deep love for 24,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness from the soul that was once Toma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this age, his name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is hope for a bright end to this tragic legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it lies with you alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the next part written in the Book of Twin Stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The end to this war! Something even my Prophecy can't tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's blank!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must write the rest of the pages yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was getting worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? You hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally say I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I never realized how you felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found it at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took far too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the scales the two worlds play on have come together,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they exude a brilliant white radiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:16:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a void in their hearts... or a new world altogether?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a pure white score of music...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This melody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my final song!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion's true melody, come forth from nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The song of all beginnings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To live is to engrave your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To hammer the melody of your life into the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will open your path.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would never have imagined this was possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I could play out my life to help someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My song...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Cayenne?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know just how you feel right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legends are written using spilled blood as ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another page of the next legend has just been written.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A physical body is such a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! That's not my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you take my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will make a fine vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, I can realize my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My domain is the shadows of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a Wingless to host an angel is a rare gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run anymore, Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender and hand over the true Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Izumo! You're not getting my wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my smelly wench and no one else's!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This planet's leader is crazy! We have to beat him or the fighting will never stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the Wings of the Sun, Solar Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got Apollo's soul! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It actually came!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wings of the Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare oppose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's begin telling...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.38,0:22:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a real legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{oh god yes not Yunoha ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.42,0:24:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is close your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.25,0:24:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to go back to a warm, peaceful morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.54,0:24:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to keep my eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.44,0:24:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life may be a struggle, but I'm holding onto mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{title: Song of Legend}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{next title: ephemera}{it's in English}
